snippet.title: Monument Valley
snippet.description: With jaw-dropping artistic level design and challenges people of all ages can enjoy, Monument Valley is well worth your money.

snippet.title: HBO brings 'Silicon Valley' to Silicon Valley
snippet.description: The network gives the tech hub a sneak peak at the new comedy series created by the man behind "OfficeSpace" and "Beavis and Butt-head."

snippet.title: Monument Valley is like a work of art (pictures)
snippet.description: Using level design that's heavily influenced by artist M.C. Escher, this puzzle game is a joy to play.

snippet.title: HBO's 'Silicon Valley': At play in the fields of the techies
snippet.description: The premiere of HBO's most anticipated series offered naivete, brutality, hope and despair. No, we're not talking about "Game of Thrones." We're talking about Mike Judge's "Silicon Valley."

snippet.title: The Silicon Valley of 'Betas'
snippet.description: Amazon's second original show drops the audience in the middle of the country's tech hub. Here's what the makers got right (hoodies, they're everywhere) and wrong (physical Bitcoins, not so much).

snippet.title: Disney, channeling Silicon Valley, launches startup accelerator
snippet.description: Working with Techstars, the media giant is forming 10 startups with mentors like CEO Bob Iger and giving them access to Disney's IP.

snippet.title: Secretary of Commerce Penny Pritzker friends Silicon Valley
snippet.description: "For us to keep up with your pace of change, this leadership team is breaking down silos throughout our agency," she tells a group of tech execs. The 47,000-person agency is conducting its own "mashup."

snippet.title: Obama's commerce secretary to petition Silicon Valley on jobs
snippet.description: Secretary Penny Pritzker will meet with LinkedIn CEO Jeff Weiner on Monday, and Facebook and others after that.

snippet.title: A historic airfield in the heart of Silicon Valley (pictures)
snippet.description: Moffett Federal Airfield and Hangar One, located in the heart of Silicon Valley, have a history that dates back to long before the tech bubble.

snippet.title: With ‘Silicon Valley,’ ‘Office Space’ creator pokes holes in tech’s shiny exterior
snippet.description: HBO gave a sneak peek in its show’s namesake to see if people from the iconic tech hub can take a joke. Turns out they can.
